metadata.name: The Power of God Anime
metadata.description:
Don't Fuck with Me! I have the power of God AND Anime on my side! AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!

In 2017 this now infamous video was taken of Me, Matt Maurer, outside of my middle school. After being posted on twitter and racking up over 9+ million views the video (for some reason) has reached a level of high tier meme status. 

This is the original 1/1 video and you now have the opportunity to own a piece of meme history yourself!

Become the sole wielder of the awesome power that is the Power of God and Anime. 

MP4 - 720x1280
